{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKHKDFKeyGenerator","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKHKDFKeyGenerator","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"14.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"iPadOS","introducedAt":"14.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"Mac Catalyst","introducedAt":"14.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false}],"title":"SBSDKHKDFKeyGenerator","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKHKDFKeyGenerator","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A key generator that uses the HMAC based HKDF algorithm to generate a new encryption key. SHA512 is used as the hash function."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The key generation consists of two phases: extraction and expansion."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"During the extraction a pseudo random key is generated from the input key material and an optional salt."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The expansion phase uses the pseudo random key and the info data block to derive the final key."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/objc(cs)NSObject"]},{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKStorageCryptingKeyGenerator","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/SQ","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/SH"]}],"schemaVersi